  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="KC11">
<l>aṉpaṉ taṉṉai yaṭaintavarkaṭ kellā</l>
<l>maṉpaṉ teṉ kurukūr nakar nampik</l>
<l>kaṉpaṉāy maturakavi coṉṉa col</l>
<l>nampuvār pati vaikuntaṅ kāṇmiṉē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>See Vaikunta as the abode of those who trust</l>
<l>in the words of Maturakavi who is [full of] love</l>
<l>for the Lord of the city of southern Kurukūr who is [full of] love</l>
<l>for all who take refuge in him who is [the object] of love!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
